data.description: This spectacular home is located in the highly sought-after community of Carino Estates.  No expense has been spared in updating this 4 bedroom/3 bath 2350 sq ft home.  Recent upgrades include 2 new HVAC units, new flooring, updated kitchen & baths, & pool updates just to name a few.  Soaring ceilings lend an air of spaciousness. The formal living room and family room provide plenty of space for relaxing & entertaining. The kitchen has been beautifully updated with quartz countertops, soft-close cabinets, stainless appliances, breakfast bar & island. There is a bedroom & full bath downstairs that is perfect for guests. The master suite features a large walk-in shower, double sinks, & 2 walk-in closets.  Step outside into the oversized back yard & enjoy your own private oasis with it's sparkling heated pool and spa, covered patio & large grassy area. The extended length garage provides plenty of space for parking & storage. There's also an RV gate and a large parking slab for your toys. Situated on a North/South cul-de-sac lot with no neighbors behind for extra privacy and within easy access of the 202, 101 & I10 freeways.  *5.7% interest rate 617k loan, only VA Assumable.*
